-- Arriva Says Scheme Shareholders Approve Takeover Offer From Deutsche Bahn
-- Mike Gavin
-- 2010-06-17T15:37:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-17/arriva-says-scheme-shareholders-approve-takeover-offer-from-deutsche-bahn.html

          
          
             Arriva Plc said that at a court
meeting and a general meeting of scheme schareholders concerning
a recommended acquisition by a Deutsche Bahn AG unit, all the
resolutions were supported by scheme shareholders.  
          
          


  


        